intro: Discover the amazing Ireland through colorful puzzle adventure!
description:
Explore the culture and beauty of Ireland with Puzzle Vacations: Ireland, a simple yet rewarding game for puzzle lovers of all kinds! 
With tons of challenging puzzles to choose from, stunning scenery to enjoy, and a little luck of the Irish, this could be the most epic vacation yet!

- Choose from 33 unique puzzle types!
- Tons of vibrant photos from an inspiring Irish holiday!
- No locked levels, so you can play at your own pace!
